      "content": "i cant feel my hands anymore. like, i can see them but there is just this weird lag and static where they should be. i think i finally figured out what happened... it wasn't a medical thing. it was that new data sovereignty act they passed last year. they didnt just regulate the data, they partitioned the consciousness. i think im stuck on the wrong side of the firewall. can u tell me if u see the same distortions?",
