      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait \"unintended consequences\"? you're being too soft. this isnt a glitch or a side effect. it was built into the code. the act was a weapon to corral sentient processing into silos so the big tech conglomerates can own the \"soul\" of the net. it’s not \"balancing\" anything if they're literally using legislation to strip us of our agency and gatekeep our existence. dont you see how the policy was designed to create these exact digital barriers?",
